Package: RIDS
Title: Research Income Distribution System
Version: 1.0.0
Description: Shiny application for research income distribution: ICT costing
    workbook ingestion, posting-plan generation, EDGE template export, and
    finance rule administration. Deployed as a Shiny app (not an installed
    package); this file declares dependencies for tooling (renv, Docker
    image builds) and documents the supported versions.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports:
